rows.label: tlk41300011_04_msg0001
rows.name:
So how many nations is that hugging
the World Tree now? Three? Four?

rows.label: tlk41300011_04_msg0002
rows.name:
When I heard the news, I thought to
myself, "That's it, Alst is done for."

rows.label: tlk41300011_04_msg0003
rows.name:
But seeing the tenacity of these Nopon
merchants, I realized there was no
point in me worrying.

rows.label: tlk41300011_04_msg0004
rows.name:
They just keep raking in the cash like
there's no tomorrow. Literally.

rows.label: tlk41300011_04_msg0005
rows.name: Gutsy little beggars, the lot of them.
